## 🌱 Use Case

This system helps farmers, students, and agricultural planners to make data-driven decisions for crop selection, improving productivity and sustainability.

---

## ⚠️ Note

* Weather data is fetched using OpenWeatherMap API
* Dataset is realistic but not official government data
* Results are AI-based suggestions (not guaranteed outcomes)

